1143
01:00:13,022 --> 01:00:15,775
Manis sekali.

1144
01:00:15,859 --> 01:00:19,696
Bagimu, birnya pasti terasa seperti madu.

1145
01:00:19,779 --> 01:00:20,655
Kenapa?

1146
01:00:21,156 --> 01:00:22,282
Karena I-jun.

1147
01:00:22,866 --> 01:00:25,743
Kudengar dia mendapat penghargaan
di kontes matematika.

1148
01:00:25,827 --> 01:00:29,080
Biasa saja. Dia juara kedua
di Provinsi Gangwon.

1149
01:00:29,164 --> 01:00:30,331
Sementara itu, Ju-ri…

1150
01:00:31,666 --> 01:00:33,960
makin lama makin tak mau belajar.

1151
01:00:34,627 --> 01:00:37,964
Tidak apa-apa. Kau tak perlu cemas.

1152
01:00:38,047 --> 01:00:40,383
Karena Ju-ri cantik.

1153
01:00:40,467 --> 01:00:42,343
Tentu saja.

